Match.com is the #1 dating site with MORE DATES & RELATIONSHIPS than any other site. Download our FREE app and see who’s single near you! 

• Browse singles near you right from your phone
• Show interest by sending a free wink
• Send and receive emails (subscription required)
• See who’s viewed your profile (subscription required)

We'd love to hear your feedback about the app. Please email us at palmpre.app@match.com
